lead_paragraph: Valeri Nichushkin had a goal and an assist on his 21st birthday, and the Dallas Stars stopped a four-game slide with a 4-2 victory over the New Jersey Devils on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Nichushkin Scores on 21st Birthday, Stars Beat Devils 4-2
